#### ‚ö†Ô∏è Important Notes

1. **Dual usage** - Works as both template helpers AND JavaScript functions
2. **Template syntax** - Use named parameters: `{{formatCurrency @model.price currency="EUR"}}`
3. **Always provide fallbacks** - Handle null/undefined gracefully
4. **Size matters** - Use compact sizes in grids, full sizes in details
5. **Respect user locale** - Check user preferences before browser defaults
6. **Don't use in computeVia** - Keep field data in its raw form
7. **Import enables both modes** - Destructuring formatters makes them available as template helpers

**Remember:** Formatters enhance display without changing your data structure!

### Utility Helpers
**Import:** `import { cn, optional, pick } from '@cardstack/boxel-ui/helpers';`

**Class Names (cn):**
```hbs
<div class={{cn "base-class" (hash active=@model.isActive error=@model.hasError)}}>
```

**Optional Actions:**
```hbs
<Button @onClick={{optional @onSave}}>Save</Button>
```

**Event Value Extraction:**
```hbs
<input {{on "input" (pick "target.value" @updateValue)}}>
```
